The '''Hongjiadu Dam''' is a concrete face rock-fill [[embankment dam]] on the [[Liuchong River]] in [[Qianxi County, Guizhou|Qianxi County]], [[Guizhou Province]], [[China]]. The dam is {{Convert|179.5|m|ft|0}} tall and was built for the purposes of [[hydroelectric]] power generation and water supply. The dam supports a 600 [[megawatt|MW]] and withholds a {{Convert|4947000000|m3|acre.ft|0}} reservoir.<ref name="chincold">{{cite web|title=Hongjiadu Hydropower Project|url=http://www.chincold.org.cn/dams/rootfiles/2010/07/20/1279253974061075-1279253974063421.pdf|publisher=Chinese National Committee on Large Dams|accessdate=8 January 2011}}</ref>
